---
layout: base.njk
title: "Ministries"
description: "Find your place at Gomer Faith Ministries — Men's, Women's, Children's, Youth, Discipleship, Evangelism, and Prayer & Bible Study ministries in Leyton, London."
nav: ministries
permalink: /ministries/
---
<section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:60px;">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">There's a place for you</span>
    <h1>Find your people.</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="max-width:60ch;">Whether you're new to faith, raising a family, mentoring a teenager, or looking for people to pray with, Gomer has a ministry built for exactly where you are.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-3 reveal">
      {% for m in collections.ministries %}
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-art"><img src="{{ m.data.image }}" alt="{{ m.data.title }}" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <span class="card-tag">{{ m.data.tag }}</span>
          <h3>{{ m.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ m.templateContent | safe }}</p>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact/">Join this ministry →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dim">
  <div class="container two-col">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">In the community</span>
      <h2>{{ homepage.outreach_headline }}</h2>
      <p class="lead">{{ homepage.outreach_text }}</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-art reveal" style="aspect-ratio:4/3;">
      <img class="hero-photo" src="{{ homepage.outreach_image }}" alt="Gomer community outreach">
      <div class="hero-art-caption">Community outreach, Leyton</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="next-step reveal">
      <div>
        <h2>Not sure where to start?</h2>
        <p>Tell us a bit about you and we'll point you to the right ministry.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
